article.description: Javonte Perkins had 25 points as Saint Louis topped VCU 80-62 on Friday night.
article.headline: Perkins scores 25 to lead Saint Louis over VCU 80-62
article.linkText: Perkins scores 25 to lead Saint Louis over VCU 80-62
article.story: ST. LOUIS -- Javonte Perkins had 25 points as Saint Louis topped VCU 80-62 on Friday night. Hasahn French had 18 points for Saint Louis (19-8, 8-6 Atlantic 10 Conference). Terrence Hargrove Jr. added 11 points. Jordan Goodwin had 10 points. Marcus Santos-Silva had 11 points for the Rams (17-10, 7-7), who have now lost four consecutive games. De'Riante Jenkins added 10 points. Saint Louis plays Saint Joseph's at home on Wednesday. VCU faces UMass on the road on Wednesday. --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
